   GORE-FATHER _ WASHINGTON _ In his travels across the country in
pursuit of the presidency, Al Gore's constant companion is his
father. In the year since Al Gore Sr. died, the obedient son rarely
gives a speech in which the stern, exacting father is not praised,
both as a parent and a politician. (Shepard, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 25. WITH PHOTOS.
