<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    LETTER FROM KOSOVO: LISTENING TO THE SWEET SOUND OF FREEDOM
 &HT;    With photo mug of Roughton.
 &HT;    Moving in both (i) International and (k) Commentary categories.
 &HT;    By BERT ROUGHTON JR. 
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service 
