Conrad III, 47, probably was born 50 years too late. He is much
more at home with the expatriate spirit of his idols, Ernest
Hemingway, F. Scott Fitzgerald and their favorite Lost Generation
couple, Gerald and Sara Murphy (Fitzgerald's models for Nicole and
