lady. She's got prestige but no power, and she is not supposed to
upstage the president, the first lady or her husband, the vice
president. That doesn't leave much room to be useful, but she is
trying with crusades for the homeless and the mentally ill. And
she's out campaigning to become first lady herself. By MARIANNE
MEANS.
</P>
