<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-11-30 17:07 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5258 &Cx1f; taf-z
u e BC-CLOUD-FILM-REVIEW-NYT     11-30 0588
