 CHRON   These are the stories The San Francisco Chronicle Food section
plans to move Tuesday, November 30, on the New York Times wire.
Questions? Please call Lesli Neilson at 415-777-8402. &HT;     
 
SAN FRANCISCO _  SUSHI  _ All around the Bay Area, sushi
restaurants are filled to capacity. And it's popularity goes beyond
restaurants _ it's in e supermarkets, on school cafeteria menus and
at sporting events. Sushi has become America's new fast food. 
Main story followed by sushi glossary, how to eat sushi, and school
for sushi chefs. 
