<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-11-30 18:07 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5319 &Cx1f; ttj-z
u w BC-NAVY-VIEQUES-HNS &LR;      11-30 0746
