   &UR; FLASH &LR;
</P>
<P>
   _ The Middleburg (Va.) Tennis Club is not offering a float in
this year's Middleburg Christmas parade, says Washingtonian
magazine, because club members feel they are not welcome. Last
year's float featured club member  &UR; Brit Hume &LR; , playing himself,
