<P>
   (NYT45) SAN MATEO, Calif. -- Nov. 30, 1999 --
GUPTA-MANAGEMENT-BOSS, 11-30 -- Umang Gupta, chief executive of
Keynote Systems Inc., a company in San Mateo that measures Web site
performance for e-commerce companies. ``I had no entrepreneurial
ambitions until I came to America,'' he writes. ``I'd love to say I
was one of those kids who set up a lemonade stand or had a paper
route. But I didn't. I just wanted a job that paid more than my dad
earned as a civil servant in India.'' (Librado Romero/New York
Times Photo) LITE
</P>
<P>
   (NYT44) SEATTLE -- Nov. 30, 1999 -- TRADE-TALKS-SCENE-2, 11-30
