on Tuesday. The WTO began its ministerial meeting on Tuesday in the
face of one of the nation's largest protests in years, with
demonstrators paralyzing downtown Seattle by blocking intersections
and staging a raucous march with tens of thousands of people. (Paul
Brown/Seattle Post-Intelligencer)
