<P>
   (NYT2) HUNTSVILLE, Texas -- Nov. 30, 1999 --
JUVENILE-EXECUTION-2-BOS-B&AMP;W, 11-30 - Randy Arroyo, 20, at the
Texas Department of Criminal Justice Ellis Unit One Prison, 12
miles outside Huntsville. Arroyo was convicted and sentenced to
death in March 1997 for the murder of US Air Force Captain Jose
Cobo during a carjacking in San Antonio. (Stan Grossfeld/Boston
Globe Photo)
</P>
<P>
   (NYT1) HUNTSVILLE, Texas -- Nov. 30, 1999 --
JUVENILE-EXECUTION-1-BOS-B&AMP;W, 11-30 - Michael Lopez, 18, at the
Texas Department of Criminal Justice Ellis Unit One Prison, 12
miles outside Huntsville. Lopez was sentenced last year to die for
the murder of a constable. He now professes his innocence and says
the shooting was accidental. (Stan Grossfeld/Boston Globe Photo)
</P>
<P>
   The New York Times News Service
</P>
